GG_BulletProof : Creator HaZarD SFD a.k.a CDG

Bulletproof is a good 10 on 10 map but I have allowed for up to 30 total players.
There is a buyzone as well for regular game mode.

This map is called Bulletproof because only the thick blue walls and Orange panels are bullet resistant.  Other than that you can be killed if you hide behind a wall and enough bullets are fired.

Gun damage is greatly reduced passing through windows or walls.
